{"title":"士兵在冬季","authors":["平启和"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":1,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵在冬季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平启和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵以梅的心境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入冬季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着漫天飞舞的雪花走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的品质"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总需要一种很贴切的象征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在冬季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有梅一样的芬芳和高洁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬季是我们很好的生长季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在军旗和铜质的号声带领下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们迎着凛冽的寒风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与夏天一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茁壮和生机勃勃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们富饶的国土上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季都不缺的是丰收景象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入冬季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的军徽多么像一朵梅花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总爱在雪野中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红地在枪旁开放"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}